properties.abstract: Itinerary offering splendid views of Leysin and Lake Geneva. Don't miss ancient village Panex, which is crossed by the famous salt path or, at the end of the trip, the beautiful vineyards and Ollon village.
properties.description:
Descent of medium difficulty alternating between forest paths and Alpine paths in the first part offering splendid views of Leysin and Lake Geneva. Don’t miss the ancient village Panex which is crossed by the famous salt path.

After passing two sections with flat trails, one between the Tailles quarry and Ecovets, the other between Panex and Ollon, you will behold the superb vineyards and Ollon village which deserves a detour.
properties.name: Office du Tourisme de Villars
properties.title: Bretaye-Ollon Bike
